can't be. Let's see. Do you remember any, let's 
talk about people that you wish you could thank.

05:57.529 --> 06:02.074
Faculty members that really you remember with 
pride, joy, gratitude? The one with anger, I can't

06:02.114 --> 06:08.422
remember his name. Actually, you know, I, I 
really, really had...

