I mean, I could probably go down the list of... Who 
would you want to thank most? Who were at the top of

06:21.815 --> 06:23.096
the list? Your gratitude. I guess probably 
thanking most would be... This is dangerous

06:27.880 --> 06:30.943
because a lot of these people are still alive.

06:33.645 --> 06:38.610
But I guess probably...

