07:11.187 --> 07:19.181
his capacity. But then within that mix, you got 
Carol Nadair, who really was the one who sort of

07:19.762 --> 07:25.652
held with student government in particular. And 
frankly, I served as student body president

07:26.634 --> 07:35.710
during that period of time when Dr. Williams was 
ill. And Clyde Freeman was acting president of

07:36.382 --> 07:43.090
Texas A&M University during the time that I was 
student vice president. And I used to kid him and

07:43.150 --> 07:48.136
say that we got away with murder because all he was 
concerned about was finance anyway. So

07:48.176 --> 07:56.746
therefore, we could get away with whatever we 
wanted, even though I had great times with Jack

